item.title: Problems with cache uploader
item.dc:creator: @belhelmiel belhelmiel
item.description:
@belhelmiel wrote:

It’s cachedownloader.java and the problem isn’t the download link. It’s something else I’ve been looking for a solution and trying to help other people too. The easiest way to fix it is to tell your players to download the cache and put it in the C drive folder on My Computer/Computer. :3 Good luck
